## chart primary-flows Primary User Flows
```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
  participant G as Graphed agent
  participant I as Inschneidergram API
  participant P as Delivery provider
  participant C as Creator
  G->>I: POST /campaigns
  I->>I: validate, normalize, suppress, schedule
  G->>I: POST /campaigns/:id/approval-workbench
  I->>I: persist creator and copy approvals
  G->>I: claim, skip, or block approved candidates
  G->>I: POST /campaigns/:id/executions
  I->>I: stored approval + operator state gates, safe adapter, proof pack
  G->>I: POST /manual-events for operator evidence when manual
  I->>P: hand off approved send intent when adapter is real
  P->>C: Instagram DM
  C-->>P: reply
  P-->>I: provider event
  I-->>G: status or webhook
```

## chart lifecycle Campaign Lifecycle
```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> queued
  queued --> running: provider sends first target
  running --> completed: all targets terminal
  running --> failed: no actionable targets remain
  queued --> failed: all targets blocked or duplicate
  completed --> [*]
  failed --> [*]
```

